/p><p style=\"margin-left:28px\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">[16]&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">唐燕</span>, <span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">许景权</span>. <span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">城市设计制度创新的策略和途径</span>. <span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">城市问题</span>, 2011(4): 16-21.</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">[17]&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">唐燕</span>. <span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">德国大都市区的区域管治案例比较</span>. <span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">国际城市规划，</span>2010(6): 58-63.</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">[18]&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">唐燕</span>, <span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">吴唯佳</span>. <span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">城市设计制度建设的争议与悖论</span>. <span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">城市规划，</span>2009(2)<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">：</span>72-77.</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">[19]&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">唐燕</span>. <span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">柏林</span>-<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">勃兰登堡都市区</span>:<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">跨区域规划合作及协调机制</span>. <span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">城市发展研究</span>, 2009(1): 49-54.</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">[20]&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">唐燕</span>. <span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">鲁尔工业区棕地复兴策略</span>. <span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">国际城市规划，</span>2007(3)<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">：</span>66-68.</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">[21]&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">唐燕</span>. <span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">村庄布点规划中的文化反思</span>: <span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">以嘉兴凤桥镇村庄布点规划为例</span>.<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">规划师，</span>2006(4): 49-52.</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">[22]&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">唐燕</span>. <span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">经济转型期城市规划决策及管理中的寻租分析</span>. <span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">城市规划，</span>2005(1)<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">：</span>25-29.</span></p><p style=\"margin-left:28px\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">[23]&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">贺静，唐燕，陈欣欣</span>. <span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">新旧街区互动式整体开发</span>:<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">我国大城市传统街区保护与更新的一种模式</span>. <span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">城市规划，</span>2003(4)<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px;\">：</span>57-60.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 1px 0px 1px 49px; line-height: 16px; break-after: avoid;\"><br></p> </div>\n</div>\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"footFollow\">\n    <div class=\"title\">——<em>关注我们</em>——</div>\n    <ul>\n        <li><a href=\"javascript:;\"><img src=\"/sites/image/nimg42_1.png\" alt=\"\"></a>\n            <div class=\"layer\"><img src=\"/sites/image/img198.png\" alt=\"\"></div>\n        </li>\n        <li><a href=\"\"><img src=\"/sites/image/nimg42_2.png\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"foot\">\n    <div class=\"wal\">\n        <div class=\"logo\">\n            <div><a href=\"https://www.tsinghua.edu.cn/publish/thu2018/index.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"/sites/image/img40_1.png\" alt=\"\"></a></div>\n            <div><a href=\"/column/INDEX\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"/sites/image/img40_2.png\" alt=\"\"></a